wikipedia_page.main: James William Kelly (born 2 May 1957) is an English former footballer. His regular position was as a midfielder. He was born in Carlisle, Cumbria. He played for Manchester United, Chicago Sting, Tulsa Roughnecks, Los Angeles Aztecs, and Toronto Blizzard.
